OH!

268
00:13:55,201 --> 00:13:58,572
[NUREHA] WHY DON'T YOU BE QUIET
AND COME WITH ME, SHIROE?

269
00:13:58,672 --> 00:13:59,906
[SHIROE] UHH...

270
00:14:00,006 --> 00:14:02,075
[NUREHA] OH, WHY NOT?

271
