BECAUSE NONE OF WHAT
YOU'RE SAYING IS TRUE.

272
00:14:05,245 --> 00:14:08,148
OK. IF I TELL THE TRUTH,
WILL YOU CHANGE YOUR MIND?

273
00:14:08,248 --> 00:14:10,617
I CAN'T SAY THAT
UNTIL YOU TELL ME.

274
00:14:12,118 --> 00:14:15,421
[NUREHA] OF COURSE, IF THAT'S
WHAT YOU REALLY WANT.

275
00:14:15,522 --> 00:14:19,459
THOUGH I ASSURE YOU, THE TRUTH
IS NOTHING YOU WANT TO HEAR.

276
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:23,429
BUT THEN AGAIN, YOU ARE
A SPECIAL BREED, AREN'T YOU?

277
00:14:23,897 --> 00:14:25,331
[SHIROE] HMM.

278
00:14:25,431 --> 00:14:28,669
I WAS SO PLAIN...
REALLY JUST A SIMPLE WOMAN.

279
00:14:28,769 --> 00:14:30,003
[SHIROE] UH...

280
00:14:30,103 --> 00:14:31,572
[NUREHA] I NEVER STOOD
OUT IN THE CROWD.

281
00:14:31,672 --> 00:14:35,075
IT WAS AS THOUGH I WERE
NOTHING MORE THAN THE AIR.

282
00:14:35,175 --> 00:14:38,044
NO ONE KNEW ME NOR
REMEMBERED MY NAME.

283
00:14:38,144 --> 00:14:41,447
NO ONE EVER EVEN NOTICED
IF I WAS THERE OR NOT.

284
00:14:42,182 --> 00:14:43,984
AND THEN IT HAPPENED.

285
00:14:44,084 --> 00:14:46,787
THEN I DISCOVERED
"ELDER TALES."

286
00:14:46,887 --> 00:14:49,723
I THOUGHT THAT HERE
IT WOULD CHANGE.

287
00:14:49,823 --> 00:14:51,792
SOMEONE MIGHT SEE ME.

288
00:14:51,892 --> 00:14:55,228
