MIGHT NEED ME.

289
00:14:55,328 --> 00:14:59,199
BUT NO. IT WAS NO DIFFERENT
HERE THAN IN REALITY.

290
00:14:59,299 --> 00:15:03,670
NO MATTER WHERE YOU ARE, THE AIR
IS STILL NOTHING BUT AIR.

291
00:15:04,938 --> 00:15:06,339
HOWEVER...

292
00:15:06,439 --> 00:15:10,677
THERE WAS ONE PERSON OUT THERE
WHO SEEMED TO NOTICE ME.

293
00:15:10,777 --> 00:15:15,015
HE KNEW WHO I WAS. HE TOLD
ME THINGS, LIKE THAT
I WAS TALENTED.

294
00:15:15,115 --> 00:15:20,587
