THAT PART UP.

299
00:15:35,001 --> 00:15:36,369
[SHIROE] BUT WAIT... WHY?

300
00:15:36,469 --> 00:15:39,305
[NUREHA] OH, SHIROE,
IS IT NOT TRUE

