IT'S A WAY BACK YET,

308
00:16:00,260 --> 00:16:03,496
[SHIROE] ONLY THAT IT CAN
MAKE SOMEONE DISAPPEAR.

309
00:16:03,597 --> 00:16:06,266
[NUREHA] DON'T YOU THINK THAT
IF YOU WORKED WITH ME,

310
