CHANCE FOR YOU TO HELP

318
00:16:28,622 --> 00:16:31,658
ALL THE WORLD'S POOR
LOST ADVENTURERS.

319
00:16:31,758 --> 00:16:34,027
(SHIROE GRIMACES)

320
