[NUREHA] AND YOU KNOW THAT
I REALLY WILL DO ANYTHING
YOU WANT, SHIROE...

333
00:17:11,932 --> 00:17:14,034
WHATEVER YOU NEED
ME TO DO FOR YOU.

334
00:17:14,134 --> 00:17:17,137
AND WHATEVER YOU WANT
ME TO DO FOR YOU.

335
00:17:17,237 --> 00:17:20,574
[NUREHA] I WILL GIVE IT
TO YOU, WHATEVER YOU WANT.

336
00:17:21,908 --> 00:17:23,209
BUT WHY?

337
00:17:23,309 --> 00:17:25,779
