TO ACHIEVE ALL YOUR DESIRES.

339
00:17:31,184 --> 00:17:34,120
[NUREHA] MAKE ME
YOUR EXCUSE.

340
00:17:35,956 --> 00:17:38,091
[SHIROE] MY REASON...

341
00:17:38,191 --> 00:17:40,326
(SLAP)
[NUREHA] AH!

342
00:17:41,962 --> 00:17:43,096
[NUREHA] SHIROE?

343
00:17:43,196 --> 00:17:45,098
