BEING AWESOME EVER!

418
00:21:25,285 --> 00:21:27,554
(LAUGHTER)

419
00:21:28,589 --> 00:21:29,756
[TOYA] OK, SO TELL US!

420
00:21:29,856 --> 00:21:32,458
WHAT ARE WE GONNA
BE DOING, SHIROE?

421
00:21:32,559 --> 00:21:35,095
[MINORI] ARE WE GONNA BE
REBUILDING THE OTHER TOWNS?

422
00:21:35,195 --> 00:21:37,598
[RUDY] WHY DON'T WE MAKE
THE ENTIRE YAMATO ISLAND CHAIN

423
00:21:37,698 --> 00:21:40,466
RIDICULOUSLY GORGEOUS? LIKE ME!

424
00:21:40,567 --> 00:21:42,603
[MINORI] WELL, NO MATTER
WHAT WE END UP DOING,

425
00:21:42,703 --> 00:21:45,606
WE NEED TO START
RAISING OUR LEVELS.

426
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:48,842
(GIANT GROWLS)

427
00:21:48,942 --> 00:21:53,113
[NYANTA] PERHAPS WE SHOULD
FIND A WAY TO GO BACK
TO OUR OWN WORLD.

428
00:21:53,213 --> 00:21:54,715
[ALL] HUH?

429
00:21:54,815 --> 00:21:55,749
[SHIROE] NO.

430
00:21:55,849 --> 00:21:58,619
WE'RE DOING SOMETHING
BIGGER THAN THAT.

431
00:21:58,719 --> 00:22:02,656
[NAOTSUGU] OH, YEAH?
WHAT'S BIGGER THAN THAT?

432
00:22:02,756 --> 00:22:05,759
[SHIROE] EVERYONE, LISTEN TO ME.

433
00:22:05,859 --> 00:22:09,262
I KNOW THE NEXT GOAL
FOR LOG HORIZON.

434
00:22:09,362 --> 00:22:10,864
[AKATSUKI] LEAVE IT TO ME!

435
00:22:10,964 --> 00:22:12,198
RIGHT ON!

436
00:22:12,298 --> 00:22:14,434
IT'S THE END FOR YOU!

437
00:22:15,769 --> 00:22:17,838
(CLANG)

438
00:22:17,938 --> 00:22:21,775
[SHIROE, VOICE‐OVER]
THE MMORPG "ELDER TALES"...

439
00:22:22,743 --> 00:22:25,411
ONE DAY, TENS OF
THOUSANDS OF PLAYERS

440
00:22:25,512 --> 00:22:28,649
SUDDENLY FOUND THEMSELVES
TRAPPED WITHIN IT,

441
00:22:28,749 --> 00:22:32,586
WITHIN A WORLD THAT LOOKED
JUST LIKE THE GAME.

442
00:22:34,655 --> 00:22:37,157
BUT NOW IT IS OUR WORLD.

443
00:22:37,257 --> 00:22:39,059
(COINS CLINK)

444
00:22:39,159 --> 00:22:41,895
IT IS OUR REALITY.

445
00:22:41,995 --> 00:22:43,697
AND FROM HERE,

446
00:22:43,797 --> 00:22:46,867
WE WILL CHANGE IT
HOWEVER WE WANT.

447
00:24:17,858 --> 00:24:21,194
[REGAN] I'VE BEEN WAITING FOR
YOU, SHIROE. I KNEW YOU'D COME.

448
00:24:21,294 --> 00:24:22,596
[SHIROE] ACTUALLY...

449
00:24:22,696 --> 00:24:25,932
I HAVE DECIDED THAT
I'M LEAVING AKIHABARA.

450
00:24:26,032 --> 00:24:27,133
[REGAN] OH.

451
00:24:27,233 --> 00:24:31,872
HMM. WOULD IT BE TOO MUCH
TO ASK IF I JOINED YOU?

